author: Huawei
description: AI isn't just changing assignments—it's rewriting the operating system of higher education. Discover how the University of Óbuda, through a decade-long partnership with #Huawei, is deploying cutting-edge infrastructure like Cloud and Wi-Fi 7 to build an AI-ready future. In this #TransformTalks from #HUAWEICONNECT EUROPE 2025, Prof. Dr. Zoltán Rajnai reveals how AI acts as an ally, enhancing research, personalizing learning, and freeing educators to focus on what truly matters. Explore more: https://bit.ly/49aeGFn #ThisIsHuawei
title: How AI is rewriting higher education's operating system
